Information.LongDescription: There is no other apartment community in Memphis like Arbors Harbor Town. It combines the convenience and cachet of Mud Island and the thoughtful planning that is Harbor Town in one unsurpassed address.Here you can live in the shadow of the Pyramid, adjacent to all the excitement of downtown Memphis and yet set apart by the tranquil Wolf river and the mighty Mississippi.Interior features rival those of the best single-family residences: large, wood-burning fireplaces, tiled entry foyers, open kitchens with pass-throughs, an abundance of natural light, and much more. You can choose from one and two bedroom garden homes and three bedroom/den townhomes.Rich wood exteriors, with cupolas, sweeping porches and balconies evoke the grace and charm of the city's heritage.
